Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.20,0:01:04.29,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(350,448)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.79,0:01:05.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.79,0:01:05.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:01:05.87,0:01:09.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加全套配料的巨无霸至尊蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.87,0:01:09.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A King Size Ultra Krabby Supreme with the works
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.29,0:01:10.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,双层面糊炸制
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.29,0:01:10.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,double batter-fried
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.21,0:01:12.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,串在棍上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.21,0:01:12.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,on a stick
Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.63,0:01:13.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.63,0:01:13.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.01,0:01:15.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,傻子一个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.01,0:01:15.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Barnacle head
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.13,0:01:16.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.13,0:01:16.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pardon me?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.18,0:01:17.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你忘了拿蛋黄酱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.18,0:01:17.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You forgot your mayonnaise
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.93,0:01:18.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.93,0:01:18.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.85,0:01:24.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看他们吃那些垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.85,0:01:24.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at them eating that garbage
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.14,0:01:26.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,简直恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.14,0:01:26.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's disgusting
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.69,0:01:29.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我都要吐了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.69,0:01:29.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're sickening
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.73,0:01:31.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我恨蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.73,0:01:31.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hate Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.74,0:01:35.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真好笑  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.74,0:01:35.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good one, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.19,0:01:35.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.19,0:01:35.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good what?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.86,0:01:37.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,搞的好像你不知道似的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.86,0:01:37.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like you don't know
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.36,0:01:37.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你刚说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.36,0:01:37.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Saying
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.95,0:01:39.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我恨蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.95,0:01:39.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"I hate Krabby Patties"
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.82,0:01:41.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的太搞笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.82,0:01:41.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's hilarious
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.24,0:01:43.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家都爱蟹黄堡的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.24,0:01:43.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everyone loves Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.58,0:01:45.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  我不算大家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.58,0:01:45.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well, not me
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.54,0:01:48.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真会讲笑话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.54,0:01:48.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're good at that
Dialogue: 1,0:01:48.08,0:01:49.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.08,0:01:49.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, everyone
Dialogue: 1,0:01:49.21,0:01:52.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥说他不喜欢蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.21,0:01:52.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squid says he doesn't like Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.59,0:01:55.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太好笑了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.59,0:01:55.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's really good, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:01:55.67,0:01:56.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,笑死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.67,0:01:56.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's really funny
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.80,0:01:59.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不准怂恿他们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.80,0:01:59.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't encourage them
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.43,0:02:00.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们这样不会走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.43,0:02:00.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They'll never leave
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.39,0:02:01.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.39,0:02:01.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.60,0:02:03.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的很好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.60,0:02:03.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's just so funny
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.14,0:02:04.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要知道我们都说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.14,0:02:04.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know what we say
Dialogue: 1,0:02:04.47,0:02:07.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,唯一不喜欢蟹黄堡的那位
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.47,0:02:07.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The only people who don't like a Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.69,0:02:09.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从来就没尝过蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.69,0:02:09.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,have never tasted one
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.73,0:02:11.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我没错了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.73,0:02:11.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's me
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.65,0:02:12.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从来没吃过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.65,0:02:12.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never had one
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.02,0:02:13.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,永远也不会吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.02,0:02:13.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,never will
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.40,0:02:16.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.40,0:02:16.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:17.03,0:02:17.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.03,0:02:17.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:17.90,0:02:18.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你刚说什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.90,0:02:18.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.78,0:02:21.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我从来没吃过蟹黄堡  永远也不会吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.78,0:02:21.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've never had a Krabby Patty, and never will
Dialogue: 1,0:02:21.28,0:02:21.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.28,0:02:21.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:02:21.95,0:02:22.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我觉得不
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.95,0:02:22.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.58,0:02:24.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我从来没吃过蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.58,0:02:24.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've never had a Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.62,0:02:26.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这些字
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.62,0:02:26.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Those words
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.79,0:02:29.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么可能会组成那样一句话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.79,0:02:27.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is it possible to use them
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.91,0:02:29.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in a sentence together like that?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.54,0:02:33.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我从来没吃过蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.54,0:02:33.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've never had a Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.38,0:02:35.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从来没吃过蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.38,0:02:35.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never had a Krabby Patty?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.09,0:02:36.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你现在就得吃一个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.09,0:02:36.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, you've gotta have one right now
Dialogue: 1,0:02:36.88,0:02:38.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,难怪你一直都很悲惨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.88,0:02:38.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No wonder you're always so miserable
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.09,0:02:39.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给  尝一口
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.09,0:02:39.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here, try this
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.93,0:02:41.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把那个垃圾给我拿开
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.93,0:02:41.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get that garbage outta my face
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.68,0:02:44.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尝一下就会爱上的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.68,0:02:44.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you try it, you'll love it
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.81,0:02:48.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尝一口所谓食物的高辐射混球吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.81,0:02:46.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Try one of those radioactive
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.52,0:02:48.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,sludge balls you call food?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.60,0:02:52.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后你是不是要我跟派大星跳方块舞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.60,0:02:50.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Next I suppose you'll want me to go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.14,0:02:52.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,square-dancing with Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.65,0:02:53.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.65,0:02:53.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.94,0:02:56.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃嘛  你一定会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.94,0:02:56.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, you're gonna
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.28,0:02:56.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.28,0:02:56.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.19,0:02:59.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,隧道快打通  火车要进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.19,0:02:59.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Open up the tunnel, here comes the train
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.36,0:03:01.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.36,0:03:01.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.99,0:03:03.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你耳朵里面有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.99,0:03:03.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that in your ear?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.53,0:03:04.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.53,0:03:04.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quit it
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.24,0:03:05.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点  嘴巴张大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.24,0:03:05.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, open wide
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.74,0:03:09.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  就算我被困到了井底
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.74,0:03:09.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, if I were trapped at the bottom of a well
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.12,0:03:10.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,困个三年
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.12,0:03:10.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for three years
Dialogue: 1,0:03:10.25,0:03:12.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只有这个蟹黄堡能吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.25,0:03:12.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with nothing to eat but that Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.33,0:03:14.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老子也要先吃我的腿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.33,0:03:14.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd eat my own legs first
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.50,0:03:16.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就算多长几条腿也不吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.50,0:03:16.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And not just the extra ones
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.96,0:03:18.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可这个对你有益
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:18.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But it's good for you
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.71,0:03:19.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这叫有益
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.71,0:03:19.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good for you?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.59,0:03:21.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那汉堡就是个热量炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.59,0:03:21.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That thing is a heart attack on a bun
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.97,0:03:22.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是那意思  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.97,0:03:22.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.93,0:03:23.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我意思是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.93,0:03:23.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I meant
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.14,0:03:25.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对你的灵魂有益
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.14,0:03:25.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,good for your soul
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.14,0:03:29.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得了吧你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.14,0:03:29.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Puh-leez
Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.35,0:03:30.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我根本没灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.35,0:03:30.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have no soul
Dialogue: 1,0:03:35.11,0:03:36.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那好吧  就吃一半
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.11,0:03:36.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, just half
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.52,0:03:37.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.52,0:03:37.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:03:37.23,0:03:37.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,四分之一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.23,0:03:37.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A quarter?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:37.82,0:03:38.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.82,0:03:38.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.36,0:03:39.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一口
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.36,0:03:39.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One bite?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.15,0:03:39.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.15,0:03:39.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.57,0:03:42.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,闻一闻就行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.57,0:03:42.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just smell it
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.66,0:03:44.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在外面都不想要这玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.66,0:03:44.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If I didn't want it out there
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.41,0:03:48.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么会在这厕所里对这玩意感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.41,0:03:48.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what makes you think I'd find it more appealing in here?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.95,0:03:50.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜托嘛  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.95,0:03:50.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:03:50.66,0:03:51.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.66,0:03:51.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.75,0:03:54.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃一口
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.75,0:03:54.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One bite
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.67,0:03:55.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.67,0:03:55.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.46,0:03:58.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你绝对不会后悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.46,0:03:58.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You won't be sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.50,0:03:59.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:03:59.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:03:59.84,0:04:01.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,特好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.84,0:04:01.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's delicious
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.55,0:04:02.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听好了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.55,0:04:02.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Listen, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:04:02.55,0:04:04.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你打算要这样下去多久
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.55,0:04:04.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,how long are you prepared to keep this up?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.97,0:04:08.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.97,0:04:08.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me that
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.52,0:04:10.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等我死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:10.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When I die
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.48,0:04:11.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别来玷污我的葬礼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.48,0:04:11.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you stay away from my funeral
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.02,0:04:17.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,难道我真的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:17.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do I really
Dialogue: 1,0:04:38.13,0:04:38.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.13,0:04:38.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.00,0:04:42.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个蟹黄堡可能就是最
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.00,0:04:42.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this Krabby Patty may be the most
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.84,0:04:44.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.84,0:04:44.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Horrible
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.05,0:04:45.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.05,0:04:45.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Putrid
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.13,0:04:46.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,做工粗劣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.13,0:04:46.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Poorly prepared
Dialogue: 1,0:04:46.43,0:04:47.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下贱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.43,0:04:47.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Vile
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.14,0:04:48.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,倒胃口
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.14,0:04:48.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Unappetizing
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.43,0:04:50.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蹩脚的烂三明治
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.43,0:04:50.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Disgusting excuse for a sandwich
Dialogue: 1,0:04:50.97,0:04:55.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让这玩意下肚是我此生最大的不悦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.97,0:04:53.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it has ever been my displeasure
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.43,0:04:55.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to have slither down my throat
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.10,0:04:56.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.10,0:04:56.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.65,0:04:59.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我诅咒这个蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.65,0:04:59.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I curse this Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.19,0:05:00.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有所有喜欢蟹黄堡的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.19,0:05:00.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and all who enjoy them
Dialogue: 1,0:05:00.94,0:05:05.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,趁早踏进他们应得的坟里去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.94,0:05:05.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to an early and well-deserved grave
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.99,0:05:07.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,懂我意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.99,0:05:07.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get it?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:07.74,0:05:09.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是根本没道理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.74,0:05:09.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But it doesn't make any sense
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.53,0:05:12.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡绝对质量上乘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.53,0:05:12.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Krabby Patty is an absolute good
Dialogue: 1,0:05:12.29,0:05:14.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家都无法抗拒它美味的魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.29,0:05:14.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nobody is immune to its tasty charms
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.71,0:05:16.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不算大家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.71,0:05:16.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nobody but me
Dialogue: 1,0:05:16.12,0:05:17.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你确定吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.12,0:05:17.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:17.17,0:05:19.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样看起来还不确定吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.17,0:05:19.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Does this look unsure to you?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.59,0:05:22.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确定了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.59,0:05:22.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:05:22.26,0:05:22.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.26,0:05:22.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.13,0:05:24.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在快去传话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.13,0:05:24.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now go spread the word
Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.81,0:05:34.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.81,0:05:34.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.43,0:05:37.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.43,0:05:37.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Still alive
Dialogue: 1,0:05:41.57,0:05:44.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.57,0:05:44.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So delicious
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.78,0:05:47.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,浪费了这么多年
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.78,0:05:47.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All the wasted years
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.83,0:05:53.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得再吃点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.83,0:05:53.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got to have more
Dialogue: 1,0:05:54.00,0:05:55.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得再吃点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.00,0:05:55.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got to have more
Dialogue: 1,0:05:58.54,0:05:59.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是等下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.54,0:05:59.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But wait
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.00,0:06:03.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚给他演那出  他肯定不会放过我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.00,0:06:03.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,After that performance, he'd never let me live it down
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.09,0:06:05.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得溜进去偷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.09,0:06:05.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I gotta sneak one
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.51,0:06:06.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就偷一个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.51,0:06:06.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just one
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.42,0:06:08.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后我就彻底戒掉那玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.42,0:06:08.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,then I'm off the stuff for good
Dialogue: 1,0:06:08.88,0:06:10.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该不可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.88,0:06:10.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't think it was possible
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.55,0:06:13.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能是真的有人不喜欢蟹黄堡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.55,0:06:13.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I guess some people just don't like Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.73,0:06:22.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.73,0:06:22.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:22.90,0:06:23.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么事  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.90,0:06:23.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.77,0:06:27.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来三层蟹黄堡巨无霸  上加海草面包
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.77,0:06:27.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need a Triple Krabby Supreme on a kelp bun
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.65,0:06:29.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再多加海腌椰菜然后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.65,0:06:29.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with extra sea pickle and
Dialogue: 1,0:06:30.24,0:06:31.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后烤焦  行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.24,0:06:31.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and burn it to a crisp, okay?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.99,0:06:33.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上就来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.99,0:06:33.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Coming right up
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.66,0:06:34.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟你说  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.66,0:06:34.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Listen, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.87,0:06:36.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要为之前的所作所为道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.87,0:06:36.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want to apologize for before
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.00,0:06:38.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只是想让你高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.00,0:06:38.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was only trying to make you happy
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.00,0:06:45.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但现在我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.00,0:06:45.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But now I've learned
Dialogue: 1,0:06:45.09,0:06:46.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各类人都需要得到包容
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.09,0:06:46.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,there's room for all kinds of people
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.01,0:06:51.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不必强求他们都喜欢一样的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.01,0:06:51.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and they don't all have to like the same things
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.97,0:06:56.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要消失啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.97,0:06:56.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't go
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.22,0:06:58.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然我强烈反对你的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.22,0:06:58.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,While I strongly disagree with your decision
Dialogue: 1,0:06:58.23,0:06:59.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我还是要接受
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.23,0:06:59.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I accept it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.10,0:07:02.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要知道  我可不常做这样的蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.10,0:07:02.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know, it's not often I get to make one like this
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.77,0:07:06.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要看人家咬第一口时的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.77,0:07:04.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want to see the look on their face
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.57,0:07:06.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when they take that first bite
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.19,0:07:09.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三层蟹黄堡巨无霸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.19,0:07:09.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Triple Krabby Supreme
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.07,0:07:11.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三层蟹黄堡巨无霸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.07,0:07:11.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Triple Krabby Supreme
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.07,0:07:14.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有谁点了三层蟹黄堡巨无霸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.07,0:07:14.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did somebody order a Triple Krabby Supreme?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.41,0:07:16.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肯定是走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.41,0:07:16.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They must have left
Dialogue: 1,0:07:16.49,0:07:18.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个  要不你就
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.49,0:07:18.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, uh, why don't you just uh
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.37,0:07:21.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把它放在这  人家可能会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.37,0:07:21.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,leave it out here in case they come back
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.12,0:07:21.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.12,0:07:21.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nope
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.87,0:07:24.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样特别的蟹黄堡得趁新鲜吃  而且
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.87,0:07:24.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a patty this special should be eaten fresh and
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.04,0:07:28.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有二十多分钟没吃这宝贝了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.04,0:07:26.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,well, I haven't had one of these babies
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.96,0:07:28.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in over 20 minutes
Dialogue: 1,0:07:28.05,0:07:28.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.05,0:07:28.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.63,0:07:33.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不论点餐的是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.63,0:07:33.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, whoever they were
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.26,0:07:34.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,品味都不错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.26,0:07:34.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,they had great taste
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.35,0:07:44.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那位都不知道错过什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.35,0:07:44.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They don't know what they're missing
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.19,0:07:44.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回去工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.19,0:07:44.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, back to work
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.02,0:07:47.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.02,0:07:47.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do I have to do?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:47.69,0:07:49.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,难道要从垃圾堆里翻一个来吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.69,0:07:49.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eat one out of the garbage?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.65,0:07:51.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真希望我能吃下这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.65,0:07:51.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wish I could eat this
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.24,0:07:53.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我都要撑死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.24,0:07:53.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I'm so darn full
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.66,0:07:54.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.66,0:07:54.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh well
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.53,0:07:57.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真就垃圾了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.53,0:07:57.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I had to say garbage
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.08,0:07:58.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天赐良机啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.08,0:07:58.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but okay
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.22,0:08:14.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会吧  怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.22,0:08:14.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh no, what's this doing here?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.76,0:08:16.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个蟹黄堡应该要被火化掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.76,0:08:16.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This patty should be cremated
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.35,0:08:23.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然我知道你不喜欢它
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.35,0:08:23.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know you didn't like him
Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.85,0:08:26.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但你能来参加葬礼  意义十分重大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.85,0:08:26.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but it means so much that you came
Dialogue: 1,0:08:52.67,0:08:54.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老婆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.67,0:08:54.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Honey?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:56.84,0:08:59.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我必须要把蟹黄堡弄到手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:08:59.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have got to get my hands on a Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:08:59.72,0:09:01.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁都拦不住我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.72,0:09:01.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And no one's going to stop me
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.94,0:09:10.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就在那
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.94,0:09:10.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There it is
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.99,0:09:14.45,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(792,330)}蟹黄堡保险库
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.70,0:09:20.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是见鬼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.70,0:09:20.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Holy shrimp
Dialogue: 1,0:09:20.62,0:09:22.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都不知道要从哪开始吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.62,0:09:22.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know where to start
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.70,0:09:25.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,重点就是只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.70,0:09:25.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All that matters is that it's just you
Dialogue: 1,0:09:25.04,0:09:26.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.04,0:09:26.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and me
Dialogue: 1,0:09:26.08,0:09:27.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,周围空无一人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.08,0:09:27.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and nobody
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.08,0:09:27.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.08,0:09:27.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:28.67,0:09:29.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.67,0:09:29.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is that you?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.09,0:09:30.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.09,0:09:30.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.21,0:09:33.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你来这干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.21,0:09:33.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:35.01,0:09:37.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都是凌晨三点钟来上班的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.01,0:09:37.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I always come to work at 3:00 am
Dialogue: 1,0:09:37.01,0:09:38.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在这个点来数芝麻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.01,0:09:38.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is when I count the sesame seeds
Dialogue: 1,0:09:38.80,0:09:39.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你又来这干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.80,0:09:39.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.55,0:09:41.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我忘拿我的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.55,0:09:41.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I forgot my
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.43,0:09:43.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡保险库干嘛开着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.43,0:09:43.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And why is the patty vault open?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.47,0:09:44.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.47,0:09:44.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought that
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.18,0:09:46.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你干嘛把一个蟹黄堡藏在背后了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.18,0:09:46.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And why are you holding a patty behind your back?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.52,0:09:47.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我我我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.52,0:09:47.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I-I-I-
Dialogue: 1,0:09:47.94,0:09:48.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没有藏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.94,0:09:48.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't do
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.73,0:09:50.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你干嘛这么紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.73,0:09:50.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And why are you acting so nervous?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:50.48,0:09:51.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你干嘛出这么多汗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.48,0:09:51.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And why are you sweating so much?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.86,0:09:53.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你干嘛看着这么饿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.86,0:09:53.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And why do you look so hungry?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.23,0:09:53.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.23,0:09:53.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And
Dialogue: 1,0:09:56.20,0:09:56.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  你听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.20,0:09:56.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, wait
Dialogue: 1,0:09:56.90,0:09:57.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是你想的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.90,0:09:57.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's not what you think
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.16,0:10:00.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这  这可是个天大的误会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.16,0:10:00.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Th-this is a big misunderstanding
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.07,0:10:00.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你得相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.07,0:10:00.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've got to believe me
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.78,0:10:01.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.78,0:10:01.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.74,0:10:03.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听好  我跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.74,0:10:03.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Listen, I am telling you
Dialogue: 1,0:10:03.04,0:10:04.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最好给我听好了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:04.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You better listen to me, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.79,0:10:07.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你喜欢蟹黄堡  对不对章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.79,0:10:07.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You like Krabby Patties, don't you, Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.63,0:10:12.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.63,0:10:12.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.09,0:10:13.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我承认了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.09,0:10:13.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I admit it, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:10:13.92,0:10:16.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我爱蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.92,0:10:16.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.38,0:10:20.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就知道  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.38,0:10:20.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I knew it all along, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.47,0:10:22.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有谁能抵挡得住蟹黄堡的魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.47,0:10:22.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No one can resist a Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:10:32.19,0:10:34.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  你吃多少了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.19,0:10:34.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, how many are you eating?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:34.44,0:10:35.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.44,0:10:35.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.54,0:10:48.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  不能一口气吃掉所有蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.54,0:10:48.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, you can't eat all those patties at one time
Dialogue: 1,0:10:48.33,0:10:50.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.33,0:10:50.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:10:50.17,0:10:51.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.17,0:10:51.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's gonna happen?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:51.71,0:10:53.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会爆炸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.71,0:10:53.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Am I gonna blow up?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:53.79,0:10:55.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会更惨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.79,0:10:55.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, worse
Dialogue: 1,0:10:55.00,0:10:56.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡会先跑你大腿里面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.00,0:10:56.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it'll go right to your thighs
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.51,0:10:58.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大腿嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.51,0:10:58.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My thighs?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.51,0:11:00.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后再爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.51,0:11:00.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And then you'll blow up
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.73,0:11:09.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.73,0:11:09.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.18,0:11:12.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还记得我吃的第一个蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.18,0:11:12.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I remember my first Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.52,0:11:16.23,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(263,363)}恶霸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.82,0:11:19.03,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(304,350)\frz19.45}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.82,0:11:19.03,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(450,678)\frz20.72}分镜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.82,0:11:21.53,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1096,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.24,0:11:21.53,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz19.45\pos(380,282)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.78,0:11:24.16,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz19.45\pos(330,340)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.78,0:11:24.16,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz19.45\pos(468,670)}创意总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.78,0:11:24.16,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.20,0:11:27.16,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(616,552)}滑浪学校
Dialogue: 1,0:11:55.40,0:11:56.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思  小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.40,0:11:56.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Miss
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.44,0:11:58.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都不想再打你小报告了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.44,0:11:58.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't want to have to report you again
Dialogue: 1,0:11:59.03,0:12:00.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只是想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.03,0:12:00.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was just wondering
Dialogue: 1,0:12:00.32,0:12:03.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,本子左边的作业铅笔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.32,0:12:03.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is it the "homework pencil" on the left side of the paper
Dialogue: 1,0:12:03.03,0:12:04.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要挨着考试铅笔好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.03,0:12:04.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,next to the "quiz pencil"
Dialogue: 1,0:12:04.57,0:12:06.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是要自个到右边去好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.57,0:12:06.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or over on the right side, all by itself
Dialogue: 1,0:12:06.49,0:12:06.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.49,0:12:06.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or
Dialogue: 1,0:12:06.99,0:12:08.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那铅笔怕是得要插到你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.99,0:12:08.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think it goes stuck inside your
Dialogue: 1,0:12:08.70,0:12:09.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等下  有了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.70,0:12:09.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, I got it
Dialogue: 1,0:12:09.83,0:12:13.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,考试铅笔要放这里  紧挨着作文铅笔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.83,0:12:11.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The "quiz pencil" goes right over here
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.71,0:12:13.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,next to the "essay" pencil
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.21,0:12:16.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,作文铅笔要侧着放  指到本子上面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.21,0:12:15.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And the "essay" pencil gets turned sideways
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.50,0:12:16.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,towards the notepad
Dialogue: 1,0:12:16.54,0:12:18.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,以备写作文用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.54,0:12:18.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just in case I have to write an essay
Dialogue: 1,0:12:18.13,0:12:19.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,同学们好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.13,0:12:19.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good morning, class
Dialogue: 1,0:12:20.01,0:12:21.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.01,0:12:21.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.13,0:12:23.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来的路上碰到堵车了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.13,0:12:23.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got caught in traffic on the way here
Dialogue: 1,0:12:23.09,0:12:27.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还以为我都要堵车堵一辈子  真要命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.09,0:12:23.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when that whole
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.88,0:12:26.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"I'm gonna be doing this for the rest of my life" thing
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.22,0:12:27.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,reared its ugly head
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.30,0:12:27.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.30,0:12:27.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.93,0:12:28.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.93,0:12:28.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.31,0:12:33.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总之呢  我们今天来了一位新同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.31,0:12:33.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Anyway, we have a new student starting today
Dialogue: 1,0:12:33.48,0:12:37.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就一起用满脸笑容迎接比目鱼平平吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.48,0:12:37.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So let's all put on a happy face for Flats the Flounder
Dialogue: 1,0:12:40.65,0:12:43.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟班上的同学们做自我介绍吧  平平
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.65,0:12:43.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tell the class something about yourself, Flats
Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.40,0:12:44.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.40,0:12:44.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well
Dialogue: 1,0:12:44.32,0:12:46.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我喜欢揍别人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.32,0:12:46.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I like to kick people's butts
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.78,0:12:50.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好幽默
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.78,0:12:50.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a card
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.29,0:12:52.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,平平  来挑下你的座位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.29,0:12:52.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, Flats, it's time to pick your seat
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.66,0:12:55.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爱坐哪里就坐哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.66,0:12:55.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just go ahead and sit anywhere you like
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.67,0:13:01.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  同学们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.67,0:13:01.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, class
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.01,0:13:02.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,记得上个星期
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.01,0:13:02.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,as you remember last week
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.13,0:13:04.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  我叫海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.13,0:13:04.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, I'm SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:13:05.01,0:13:06.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:06.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.26,0:13:08.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要揍你一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.26,0:13:08.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna kick your butt
Dialogue: 1,0:13:10.72,0:13:13.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第二次讲这笑话更幽默了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.72,0:13:13.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That joke was almost funnier the second time
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.52,0:13:14.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.52,0:13:14.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:13:14.98,0:13:16.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.98,0:13:16.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean it
Dialogue: 1,0:13:18.06,0:13:19.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这回的笑话怕是说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.06,0:13:19.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That time it almost seemed like
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.15,0:13:22.57,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(696,748)}我认真的
Dialogue: 1,0:13:22.57,0:13:24.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你真是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.57,0:13:24.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you did mean it
Dialogue: 1,0:13:24.49,0:13:25.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.49,0:13:25.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.49,0:13:26.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么事  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.49,0:13:26.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.74,0:13:29.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能失陪一辈子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.74,0:13:29.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I be excused for the rest of my life?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.32,0:13:31.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.32,0:13:31.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why no, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:13:31.62,0:13:34.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在讲一节枯燥到得靠咖啡提神的课
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.62,0:13:34.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm in the middle of a coffee-fueled sermon right now
Dialogue: 1,0:13:34.41,0:13:37.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这课的内容可不能漏听了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.41,0:13:37.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't afford to miss this information
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.00,0:13:38.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好的  泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.00,0:13:38.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:13:38.92,0:13:40.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起  泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.92,0:13:40.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.88,0:13:46.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在有谁自愿上台吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.88,0:13:44.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, can I please have a volunteer
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.59,0:13:46.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to come up to the board?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.34,0:13:48.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你来上吧  平平
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.34,0:13:48.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about you, Flats?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.68,0:13:50.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请你给我们画出
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.68,0:13:50.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please draw for us
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.05,0:13:53.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,基本十字路口的示意图  平平
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.05,0:13:53.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a diagram of a basic four-way intersection, Flats
Dialogue: 1,0:13:55.98,0:14:00.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快转身给全班看你画的示意图  同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:14:00.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please turn and show the class what you drew, honey
Dialogue: 1,0:14:04.32,0:14:07.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天哪  好有创意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.32,0:14:07.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My, how very creative
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.53,0:14:10.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们班出了个画家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.53,0:14:10.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We have an artist in the class
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.75,0:14:18.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我真搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.75,0:14:18.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just don't understand
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.50,0:14:20.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么平平要揍我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.50,0:14:20.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why would Flats want to kick my butt?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.38,0:14:24.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都没跟人家说够两个字
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.38,0:14:24.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I haven't said two words to the guy
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.21,0:14:27.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  我叫海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.21,0:14:27.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, I'm SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.42,0:14:28.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.42,0:14:28.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.22,0:14:28.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.22,0:14:28.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,two
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.93,0:14:30.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好  讲了七个字
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.93,0:14:30.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh no, that's three
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.93,0:14:30.80,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(850,920)}三 个
Dialogue: 1,0:14:30.80,0:14:32.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.80,0:14:32.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What am I gonna do?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.55,0:14:33.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.55,0:14:33.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.64,0:14:34.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.64,0:14:34.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Someone's coming
Dialogue: 1,0:14:34.72,0:14:35.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,离得越来越近了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.72,0:14:35.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're getting closer
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.85,0:14:37.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我必须要自然点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.85,0:14:37.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just got to act natural
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.81,0:14:42.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.81,0:14:42.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's real nice
Dialogue: 1,0:14:46.19,0:14:48.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我本来还以为来的会是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.19,0:14:48.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought for sure that was gonna be
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.03,0:14:49.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,平平
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.03,0:14:49.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Flats?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:50.03,0:14:51.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先生好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.03,0:14:51.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.07,0:14:53.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最近揍人揍得舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.07,0:14:53.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kicked any good butts lately?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.87,0:14:55.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还记得上个星期
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.87,0:14:55.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I remember last week
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.99,0:14:58.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我把那个人揍得落花流水
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.99,0:14:58.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was kickin' this guy's butt real good
Dialogue: 1,0:14:58.41,0:14:59.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个人弯下身子说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:14:59.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And he leans over and says
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.87,0:15:03.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要知道生活就像是一大水桶的木屑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.87,0:15:03.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Hey, ya know, life's like a bucket of wood shavings
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.38,0:15:05.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过如果木屑是在提桶里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.38,0:15:05.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"except for when the shavings are in a pail
Dialogue: 1,0:15:05.67,0:15:07.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那样生活就像是一大提桶的木屑了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.67,0:15:07.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,then it's like a pail of wood shavings"
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.26,0:15:10.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个故事对我好有启发
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.26,0:15:10.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That story really speaks to me
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.72,0:15:11.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.72,0:15:11.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.43,0:15:12.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,启发什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.43,0:15:12.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's it say?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:12.34,0:15:15.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,启发了我  要加倍用力来揍你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.34,0:15:15.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It says now I'm gonna kick your butt twice as hard
Dialogue: 1,0:15:19.85,0:15:22.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把小蜗的饮水盆交给小蜗保管
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.85,0:15:22.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I'll leave Gary's water bowl to Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:15:22.44,0:15:24.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把我窗帘交给
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.44,0:15:24.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and my curtains to
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.15,0:15:26.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海神王啊  我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.15,0:15:26.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Neptune, I just can't do this
Dialogue: 1,0:15:28.69,0:15:31.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,死刑犯牢房  请下一位接听电话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.69,0:15:31.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Death row, "next-in-line" speaking
Dialogue: 1,0:15:31.41,0:15:34.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂  我要订一份外卖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.41,0:15:34.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, I'd like to place an order for delivery
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.37,0:15:35.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.37,0:15:35.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:15:35.33,0:15:36.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.33,0:15:36.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is that you?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.49,0:15:37.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我啊  马里奥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.49,0:15:37.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, hey, Mario
Dialogue: 1,0:15:38.08,0:15:41.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要来份大份的加双倍橄榄  双倍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.08,0:15:41.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me get a large, double olive, double
Dialogue: 1,0:15:41.12,0:15:42.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.12,0:15:42.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, listen
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.17,0:15:43.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.17,0:15:43.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's me, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.67,0:15:44.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要你来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.67,0:15:44.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need your help
Dialogue: 1,0:15:44.88,0:15:47.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你现在是在匹萨城里上班吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.88,0:15:47.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're working at Pizza Castle now?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.09,0:15:47.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.09,0:15:47.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.96,0:15:49.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是的  你听好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.96,0:15:49.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, listen
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.30,0:15:50.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.30,0:15:50.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm in big trouble
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.51,0:15:53.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,驾校新来了个同学  想要揍我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.51,0:15:51.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's a new guy at school here
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.84,0:15:53.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and he wants kick my butt
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.47,0:15:55.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟你说  你又大又壮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.47,0:15:55.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Listen, you're big and strong
Dialogue: 1,0:15:55.30,0:15:57.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可不可以来这一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.30,0:15:57.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you think you can come down here
Dialogue: 1,0:15:57.22,0:15:58.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,帮忙来揍他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.22,0:15:58.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,maybe rough him up a bit
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.72,0:16:00.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好让他放过我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.72,0:16:00.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just to get him off my back?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.35,0:16:01.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.35,0:16:01.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.64,0:16:02.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好怕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.64,0:16:02.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm so scared
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.56,0:16:04.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我感觉我都要吐了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.56,0:16:04.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it feels like I'm gonna throw up
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.90,0:16:06.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那边店里没关门
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.90,0:16:06.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, they're not closed
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.69,0:16:08.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道你想要加橄榄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.69,0:16:08.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know, you want olives
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.53,0:16:09.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你有在听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.53,0:16:09.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, you there?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.99,0:16:11.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真对不起  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.99,0:16:11.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:16:11.36,0:16:15.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我刚在跟我社区学院的校友平平聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.36,0:16:12.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was just talking to
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.32,0:16:15.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,my old community college buddy, Flats
Dialogue: 1,0:16:15.82,0:16:19.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在汽水店里碰见他的  你说怪不怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.82,0:16:19.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I bumped into him at the soda store, isn't that funny?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.04,0:16:22.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们肯定有好几年没有碰过面了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.04,0:16:22.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It must have been years since we've seen each other
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.16,0:16:23.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.16,0:16:23.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, let me get going
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.29,0:16:25.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他得马上回驾校
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.29,0:16:25.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's got to go back to school soon
Dialogue: 1,0:16:25.42,0:16:27.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说是他必须得去揍某个人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.42,0:16:27.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He says he's got to kick somebody's butt
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.92,0:16:31.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.92,0:16:31.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:31.80,0:16:33.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是匹萨城吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.80,0:16:33.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is this Pizza Castle?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:36.80,0:16:38.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,进来  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.80,0:16:38.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come in, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.56,0:16:45.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡芙老师  我可不可以改上别的班
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.56,0:16:45.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Puff, can I be in a different class?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.15,0:16:46.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.15,0:16:46.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:46.31,0:16:47.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我说不来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.31,0:16:47.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't tell you
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.90,0:16:49.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么就说不来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.90,0:16:49.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why ever not?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.32,0:16:51.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就是说不来  泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.32,0:16:51.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just can't, Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.69,0:16:54.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就只能说  我正面临生命危险
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.69,0:16:54.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My physical being is at stake, let's just leave it at that
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.66,0:16:57.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你可以向我倾诉的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.66,0:16:57.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, you can tell me anything
Dialogue: 1,0:16:57.91,0:16:59.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要相信这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.91,0:16:59.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've got to believe that
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.45,0:17:00.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.45,0:17:00.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.29,0:17:01.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.29,0:17:01.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,okay
Dialogue: 1,0:17:01.33,0:17:03.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是必须要发誓不跟别人讲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.33,0:17:03.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But only if you promise to keep it between us
Dialogue: 1,0:17:03.79,0:17:05.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.79,0:17:05.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.00,0:17:07.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,平平说他要揍我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.00,0:17:07.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Flats says he's gonna kick my butt
Dialogue: 1,0:17:07.54,0:17:08.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.54,0:17:08.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.54,0:17:12.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的课上不准许出现揍人现象
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.54,0:17:12.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There shall be no butt-kicking in any class of mine
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.42,0:17:14.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家都老大不小了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.42,0:17:14.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is an adult program
Dialogue: 1,0:17:14.42,0:17:17.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  就交给我好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.42,0:17:17.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, just leave it to me
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.76,0:17:19.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.76,0:17:19.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:17:19.10,0:17:20.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就知道可以信任你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:20.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I knew I could count on you
Dialogue: 1,0:17:23.81,0:17:25.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,饭吃得香不香  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.81,0:17:25.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have a nice lunch, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:25.73,0:17:26.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然香  泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.73,0:17:26.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.23,0:17:30.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  我帮你跟平平讲了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.23,0:17:30.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, I talked to Flats for you
Dialogue: 1,0:17:30.90,0:17:32.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还特别提了你名字
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.90,0:17:32.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I used your name
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.28,0:17:34.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都是场误会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.28,0:17:34.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It was all a misunderstanding
Dialogue: 1,0:17:34.24,0:17:35.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.24,0:17:35.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You what?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:35.40,0:17:37.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他根本就不是要揍你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.40,0:17:37.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He was never going to kick your butt at all
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.82,0:17:39.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知道吗  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.82,0:17:39.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You see, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:17:39.20,0:17:42.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,平平是从一个只要揍别人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.20,0:17:42.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Flats is from a town where "kicking someone's butt"
Dialogue: 1,0:17:42.29,0:17:45.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就表示想要交朋友的镇上来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.29,0:17:45.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,means that he wants to be your friend
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.75,0:17:49.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那边揍别人也可能表示周末一起锻炼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.75,0:17:49.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and maybe play some sports with you on weekends
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.46,0:17:51.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我拉肚子了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.46,0:17:51.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got diarrhea
Dialogue: 1,0:17:57.01,0:17:58.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是平平他爸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.01,0:17:58.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you Flats's Dad?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.76,0:18:00.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  我就是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.76,0:18:00.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, yes, I am
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.30,0:18:00.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.30,0:18:00.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.93,0:18:02.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟你说  我不知道要怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.93,0:18:02.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See, I didn't know where else to turn
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.72,0:18:03.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星帮不了我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.72,0:18:03.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick couldn't help me
Dialogue: 1,0:18:03.89,0:18:05.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡芙老师反而让事情更严重了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.89,0:18:05.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and Mrs. Puff only made it worse
Dialogue: 1,0:18:05.68,0:18:07.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我上学就坐在你儿子平平旁边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.68,0:18:07.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I sit next to your son Flats in school
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.60,0:18:09.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他只不过是个好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:09.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and he is a fine boy and all
Dialogue: 1,0:18:09.23,0:18:10.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我其实也不太想要让你误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.23,0:18:10.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I don't want you to take this the wrong way
Dialogue: 1,0:18:10.90,0:18:12.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是他真的想要揍我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.90,0:18:12.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but he wants to kick my butt
Dialogue: 1,0:18:12.48,0:18:13.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爸  你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.48,0:18:13.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dad, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:14.44,0:18:15.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啥也没干  儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.44,0:18:15.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing, son
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.44,0:18:18.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我怎么跟你说的  不准跟陌生人讲话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.44,0:18:18.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What did I tell you about talking to strangers?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:18.70,0:18:20.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在他要揍我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.70,0:18:20.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now he's going to kick my butt
Dialogue: 1,0:18:25.62,0:18:28.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都借过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.62,0:18:28.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Out of my way
Dialogue: 1,0:18:28.08,0:18:30.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那人要揍我  看到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.08,0:18:30.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can't you see he's going to kick my butt?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:32.21,0:18:33.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们好  年轻人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.21,0:18:33.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi there, young people
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.21,0:18:35.55,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1018,326)}公交站
Dialogue: 1,0:18:33.59,0:18:35.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天真是好天气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.59,0:18:35.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice day today
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.71,0:18:38.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以说你喜欢揍人  是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.71,0:18:38.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So you like kickin' butts, do ya?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.38,0:18:40.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那咱就好好来揍你  臭老头
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.38,0:18:40.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, we'll show you, old man
Dialogue: 1,0:18:47.18,0:18:48.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.18,0:18:48.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.31,0:18:49.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得离开这个镇子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.31,0:18:49.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got to skip town
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.60,0:18:50.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开始新生活
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.60,0:18:50.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Start a new life
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.60,0:18:51.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用化名来混日子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.60,0:18:51.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Live under an assumed name
Dialogue: 1,0:18:51.98,0:18:53.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,宝宝绵海
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.98,0:18:53.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,BobPants SpongeSquare
Dialogue: 1,0:18:53.57,0:18:54.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好名字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.57,0:18:54.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's good
Dialogue: 1,0:18:54.27,0:18:55.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,长出胡子  然后再剃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.27,0:18:55.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Grow a beard and then shave it off
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.82,0:18:57.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从此过上幸福快乐的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.82,0:18:57.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and live happily ever after
Dialogue: 1,0:18:58.07,0:19:00.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是啊  不过你忘了还有我要揍你这段
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.07,0:19:00.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, except you forgot the part where I kick your butt
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.78,0:19:00.86,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1106,840)}裤头村垃圾
Dialogue: 1,0:19:23.68,0:19:26.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,平平  你好点了没
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.68,0:19:26.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Flats, you feeling better?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.14,0:19:28.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.14,0:19:28.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.18,0:19:30.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这是在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.18,0:19:30.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.10,0:19:31.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你现在是在住院
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.10,0:19:31.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, you're in the hospital
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.44,0:19:33.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这位年轻人救了你一命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.44,0:19:33.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This young boy saved your life
Dialogue: 1,0:19:33.11,0:19:36.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他连续给你做了五小时的心肺复苏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.11,0:19:36.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He performed CPR for five hours straight
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.02,0:19:36.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.02,0:19:36.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.78,0:19:39.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,医生开始几分钟就说你没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.78,0:19:39.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,they said you'd be okay after the first few minutes
Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.49,0:19:40.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过我只想确保万无一失
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.49,0:19:40.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I just wanted to be sure
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.45,0:19:42.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好感动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.45,0:19:42.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm touched
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.91,0:19:45.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等我揍你那会  我一定会记好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.91,0:19:45.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll have to remember that when I'm kicking your butt
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.37,0:19:47.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这些花是送我的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.37,0:19:47.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Those flowers for me?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:48.87,0:19:51.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他还是要揍我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.87,0:19:51.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's still gonna kick my butt
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.71,0:19:56.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到底还得教训你多少次  臭老头
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.71,0:19:53.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How many times
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.92,0:19:56.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,do we have to teach you this lesson, old man?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.75,0:19:59.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好爱年轻人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.75,0:19:59.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love the young people
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.75,0:20:01.93,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(556,496)}公交站
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.64,0:20:08.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  我还年轻不能被揍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.64,0:20:08.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, I'm too young to have my butt kicked
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.39,0:20:12.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这一生还有好多的事情没有做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.39,0:20:10.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There are so many things in life
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.35,0:20:12.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that I haven't gotten to do
Dialogue: 1,0:20:12.44,0:20:14.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请稍等  将为您的通话进行转接
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.44,0:20:14.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hang on, I'll transfer your call
Dialogue: 1,0:20:15.61,0:20:16.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.61,0:20:16.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.73,0:20:21.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,平平
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.73,0:20:21.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Flats
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.03,0:20:22.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,揍人时间到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.03,0:20:22.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's butt-kicking time
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.03,0:20:24.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  我要让你知道点事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.03,0:20:24.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, there's something I want you to know
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.87,0:20:26.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我太害怕  记不起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.87,0:20:26.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I'm too scared to remember what it is
Dialogue: 1,0:20:40.01,0:20:41.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开揍了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.01,0:20:41.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's do it
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.51,0:20:42.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗快走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.51,0:20:42.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go away, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:20:42.42,0:20:43.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不想要你看到这一幕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.42,0:20:43.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't want you to see this
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.97,0:20:45.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会很难看的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.97,0:20:45.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it'll be ugly
Dialogue: 1,0:20:47.22,0:20:48.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.22,0:20:48.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.26,0:20:49.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.26,0:20:49.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold on
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.98,0:20:53.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行了  我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.98,0:20:53.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:20:58.69,0:20:59.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都说我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.69,0:20:59.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I said, I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.70,0:21:05.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没听到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.70,0:21:05.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Didn't you hear me?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.78,0:21:06.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都说我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.78,0:21:06.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I said I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.41,0:21:10.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好痒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.41,0:21:10.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That tickled
Dialogue: 1,0:21:19.46,0:21:20.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.46,0:21:20.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.38,0:21:23.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在吸收他揍我的力  好像我是某种
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.38,0:21:23.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm absorbing his blows like I was made of some kind of
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.17,0:21:24.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,疏松材料组成的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.17,0:21:24.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,spongy material
Dialogue: 1,0:21:24.93,0:21:26.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知道什么意思了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.93,0:21:26.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And do you know what that means?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.55,0:21:29.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我明天可以去上班了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.55,0:21:29.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I get to go to work tomorrow
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.43,0:21:33.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你有七吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.43,0:21:33.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you have any sevens?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.21,0:22:02.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,平平  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.21,0:22:02.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Flats, are you okay?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.30,0:22:08.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要给我欢呼了  我的大人同学们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.30,0:22:08.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do not cheer me, my fellow adult classmates
Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.43,0:22:10.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,平平才是真正的受害者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.43,0:22:10.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Flats was the real victim here
Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.68,0:22:14.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,被社会所迫走上暴力不归路的受害者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.68,0:22:13.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A victim of a society that's riding down
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.01,0:22:14.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a violent road to nowhere
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.18,0:22:16.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我管这条不归路叫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.18,0:22:16.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a road I call
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.48,0:22:17.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,暴路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.48,0:22:17.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Violence Road"
Dialogue: 1,0:22:17.94,0:22:19.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉同学们  我迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.94,0:22:19.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late, class
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.44,0:22:19.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.44,0:22:19.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.98,0:22:24.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.98,0:22:24.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:22:24.69,0:22:28.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你居然把新同学给打趴下了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.69,0:22:28.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you beat up a new student
Dialogue: 1,0:22:28.86,0:22:31.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我现在要揍你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.86,0:22:31.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to kick your butt
